                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821204-24-off119 t17821204-24-cd120"></join> last one cotton gown, value 2 s. one Marseilles petticoat, value 2 s. one cloth apron, value 3 d. one pair of thread stockings, value 6 d. and two linen handkerchiefs, value 6 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
